reviews.review_text:
Hey it is actually a good show Despite all the bad vibes from 1995.
This show and this recording are pretty good. 
the Bird song is great and a very good second set with  some amazing chants during the drums segment. 
Peace Jerry

AWESOME RECORDING!! THANK YOU! THANK YOU! THANK YOU! 

I used to have a digital copy of this recording of this show, which I recorded from a friend of mine's DAT copy onto (the obligatory 1996 media) 3 CDs.  Many years ago I broke the first CD and the second disc stopped working. I had lost contact with the person from whom I originally gotten it, and OFTEN longed for this particularly recording of this show.

I know there are many opinions of the Grateful Dead's 1995 summer tour, but this is a great show (IMO) and this is a SUPERB recording of it!

THANK YOU so much for uploading this for all of us to enjoy.
